{"tid":144932,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你班道德貓奴撚個老母呀","createTime":"2017-03-05T23:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T09:15:12.000Z","uid":44039,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1760ee1abbe4308420d26e8a33142e2ee84073d","tid":144932,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T23:57:08.000Z","msg":"其實一直我都好憎寵物台啲奴隸獸<br />\n開口埋開叫啲樓主帶隻貓去睇獸醫<br />\n其實佢地可能平時自己睇醫生睇錯左獸醫<br />\n搞到佢地自己short short地<br />\n成日叫人做埋啲用屎眼都諗唔到既野<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n事緣：求救 隻bb貓火新入屋第一晚零晨係度亂叫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/88752/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/88752/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n上個月黎左隻街貓<br />\n一班正義貓撚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yZjZ5o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yZjZ5o.jpg&h=ca33249a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/072834_f785b8df5f2866dbecd43684db88168a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F072834_f785b8df5f2866dbecd43684db88168a.jpg&h=a47b10a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/072834_1c24379b971163ad1060ad809ab4cc4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F072834_1c24379b971163ad1060ad809ab4cc4e.jpg&h=a27f7eec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JY36W48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJY36W48.jpg&h=957a85a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/072835_4af55e06692f401a969d8673af927a6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F072835_4af55e06692f401a969d8673af927a6a.jpg&h=9f26f20e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/072845_581d45a74e9d439dcef23566e788e9b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F072845_581d45a74e9d439dcef23566e788e9b7.jpg&h=da5a65d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wRjm0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wRjm0y.jpg&h=e2e34536&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/072846_f4c92ef4d52cb65ad1ee622139c616f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F072846_f4c92ef4d52cb65ad1ee622139c616f0.jpg&h=441e1493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n最後我都係冇聽到 冇由得班痴線佬撚化我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過果隻貓（叫scream cheese 因為成日鳩叫)有求生意志<br />\n識得打開籠同貓袋拉鍊 點都攔唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然要相處下喎 咪相處下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個月多啲之後<br />\n即係今日<br />\n我隻迷人可愛大小姐 行埋黎喵我<br />\n晨早流流喵我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我伸手摸下佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一摸 條頸好多一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果下未訓醒唔撚知係咩黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvG4393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvG4393.jpg&h=eb13838b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再諗多幾諗 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由是我鼓起勇氣單人匹馬'的'左佢去沖涼<br />\n（我從未試過得我一個冇助手係度幫佢沖涼）<br />\n一用支去蝨沖涼液 果幾粒野就甩哂<br />\n咁用個屎忽唔洗獸醫都知係乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來係件開心既事<br />\n<br />\n咁啦<br />\n咁我人就得一個<br />\n我又得兩隻手<br />\n拎灑花 支沖涼 拎捉蝨梳 再捉住佢 點都要換手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係我手與手交更期間<br />\n佢一野跳撚左上我個頭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母 我成頭泡呀</span></span><br />\n咩叫<span style=\"color: blue;\">濕撚哂唔洗驚</span><br />\n我果下覺悟左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件衫扯爛埋 成腳都係抓痕<br />\n<br />\n好在我醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫佢沖涼之後 我第一時間就係打電話屌鳩我條仔唔撚識搭火箭係天水圍出黎油塘搵我<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（距離係咁 但實際地方唔撚想話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</span></span><br />\n第二樣就係上黎屌埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老母呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\nBtw, 我而家就準備訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班撚樣記得夠鐘就好去睇獸醫啦"},{"pid":"baeb492dfd290b8e4deff02c21925ae011f8daee","tid":144932,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T23:58:58.000Z","msg":"呀 唔記得講 <br />\n我有幫佢地除開蝨同杜蟲<br />\n不過咁 condom都唔係100%啦<br />\n唔係既話世伯伯母點會生左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f9b281c9f63f22f67d4e2bc0bbec8708a29456","tid":144932,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"c6a1d97d640b1dd290d143329258a0fb168242b1","tid":144932,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:02:28.000Z","msg":"留個名"},{"pid":"c